section.section:
"Incidental costs" include:
Insurance policy deductibles;
Charges for rental vehicles;
The difference between the value of a stolen vehicle at the time of theft and the cost of a replacement vehicle;
Sales taxes;
Registration fees;
Transaction fees; and
Mechanical inspection fees.

"Vehicle protection product" includes:
An alarm system;
A body part marking product;
A steering lock;
A window etch product;
A pedal or ignition lock;
A fuel or ignition kill switch; and
An electronic, radio, or satellite tracking device.
